name: The Ultimate Watch
description:
The best piece of gear for all blockchain dwellers!

- Track the time with its liquid magnetic technology.
- Bio-secure it with your fingerprint.
- Take care of your little mystical pet. Safe in its little dome.
- Don't miss out on your social media feeds.
- Keep up with the market (tezos <3)
- Stream videos, shows and movies anywhere, anytime.
- Surf the web.

and if that wasn't enough you have your personal virtual assistant "Clippany".
She's ready to help 24/7.

Includes: 1x usb port, Charging cable.

Burak Parlak, 2021

Thanks for the support<3
